# Perbandingan Tabel — ERP Staging vs BOM Design Baru

| Tanggal | 5 Juni 2026 |
|---------|-------------|
| ERP | [ERPKu Staging BOM](https://erp.stg.solusiuntuknegeri.com/manufacture/bill-of-materials) |
| App baru | BOM Design by Gemini |

---

## 1. Peta layar (high level)

```mermaid
flowchart TB
  subgraph erp [ERP Staging]
    EL[List BOM]
    EW[Wizard 4 step]
    EM[Master terpisah: Materials / WC / Routing]
  end
  subgraph app [Design Baru]
    AL[Dashboard List]
    AP[Product Panel]
    AT7[7 Tab Editor]
    AM[Master Modal 12 tab]
  end
  EL --> EW
  AL --> AP --> AT7
```

| Area UX | ERP Staging | Design Baru | Selisih utama |
|---------|-------------|-------------|---------------|
| Daftar project BOM | ✅ 1 tabel | ✅ 1 tabel | App + import Excel, HPP USD |
| Produk | ✅ Step 1 wizard (form) | ✅ Panel collapsible | App + coating m² preview |
| Struktur | ✅ Step 2 Komponen (5 grup kolom) | ✅ Tab tree + visual | App: SUBMODUL 2, Excel tipe |
| Material | ✅ Step 3 tabel bahan baku | ✅ Tab PART-only + SF/WF | App: vendor, multi-currency |
| Proses | ✅ Step 4 tabel operasi | ✅ Tab rekap + detail | App: routing steps breakdown |
| Container | ❌ Tidak ada | ✅ Tab lengkap | **Hanya app** |
| Summary | ❌ Tidak ada | ✅ Tab + nested ops | **Hanya app** |
| COGS | ❌ Tidak ada di editor | ✅ Waterfall + parity | **Hanya app** |
| FOB / Jurnal | ❌ Tidak ada | ✅ Tab ERP journal | **Hanya app** |
| Master | ✅ Modul ERP terpisah | ✅ Modal seed dummy | ERP live DB vs local seed |

